      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PERCEPTION (3) resumed in a Grade 5 at this track and ran into the frame when third over 300m (16.76). Solid record here at the distance winning three races. Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in two starts. Can find winning form. BRUNSWICK ROCKET (6) scored well last start as odds-on favourite by one length at this track in a handy 19.25 beating JULANE AVA. Awkwardly drawn but goes well at this distance. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and four minor placings to his credit. Can go close again if runs up to latest figure. CANYA CURRENCY (1) is boxed nicely on the inside. Latest effort finished 6th over 300m at this track beaten 6 lengths (17.07) behind Tuckeroo Road in a Grade 5 on July 13. Can feature in the finish. JULANE AVA (2) must be among the chances on the last run here.",
